addf4355a115).\"\n  example:\n  - \"The following example demonstrates how to programmatically add a GridViewCommandEventHandler delegate to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowCommand> event of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.  \\n  \\n [!code-cs[GridViewCommandEventHandler#1](~/add/codesnippet/csharp/t-system.web.ui.webcontr_364_1.aspx)]\\n [!code-vb[GridViewCommandEventHandler#1](~/add/codesnippet/visualbasic/t-system.web.ui.webcontr_364_1.aspx)]  \\n  \\n The following example demonstrates how to declaratively add a GridViewCommandEventHandler delegate to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowCommand> event of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.  \\n  \\n [!code-cs[GridViewRowCommmand#1](~/add/codesnippet/csharp/t-system.web.ui.webcontr_364_2.aspx)]\\n [!code-vb[GridViewRowCommmand#1](~/add/codesnippet/visualbasic/t-system.web.ui.webcontr_364_2.aspx)]\"\n  syntax:\n    content: public delegate void GridViewCommandEventHandler(object sender, GridViewCommandEventArgs e);\n  inheritance:\n  - System.Delegate\n  platform:\n  - net462\nreferences:\n- uid: System.Delegate\n  isExternal: false\n  name: System.Delegate\n"}